{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·005.1", "text_original": "中谷有蓷，暵其乾矣。有女仳離，嘅其嘆矣。嘅其嘆矣！遇人之艱難矣！", "text_normalized": "中谷有蓷，暵其乾矣。有女仳離，嘅其嘆矣。嘅其嘆矣！遇人之艱難矣！", "notes": "中谷有蓷 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·005.2", "text_original": "中谷有蓷，暵其脩矣。有女仳離，條其歗矣。條其歗矣！遇人之不淑矣！", "text_normalized": "中谷有蓷，暵其脩矣。有女仳離，條其歗矣。條其歗矣！遇人之不淑矣！", "notes": "中谷有蓷 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·005.3", "text_original": "中谷有蓷，暵其濕矣。有女仳離，啜其泣矣。啜其泣矣！何嗟及矣！", "text_normalized": "中谷有蓷，暵其濕矣。有女仳離，啜其泣矣。啜其泣矣！何嗟及矣！", "notes": "中谷有蓷 Chinese stanza 3."}
